"Movement
nnoremap <up> <c-y>
nnoremap <down> <c-e>
nnoremap <c-down> <c-d>
nnoremap <c-up> <c-u>
nnoremap <c-j> <c-e>
nnoremap <c-k> <c-y>
nnoremap } }zz
nnoremap { {zz

"Formatting
nnoremap zk maO<esc>k`a
nnoremap zj mao<esc>k`a

"Mode Changes
nnoremap <esc> :noh<return><esc>
inoremap jj <esc>

"Saving, Editing
nnoremap <Leader>ev :e $HOME\_vimrc <return>
nnoremap ;; :w<cr>
inoremap ;; <esc>:w<cr>

"Old Habits Die Hard
inoremap <backspace> <esc>xi
inoremap <c-BS> <esc>dBxi
